Package: org.ajoberstar.grgit.operation

[Groovy] Enum Mode

    • org.ajoberstar.grgit.operation.MergeOp.Mode

      • Enum Constants Summary

          Enum constants classes 
          Enum constant Description
          CREATE_COMMIT Always creates a merge commit (even if a fast-forward is possible).
          DEFAULT Fast-forwards if possible, creates a merge commit otherwise.
          NO_COMMIT Merges changes, but does not commit them.
          ONLY_FF Only merges if a fast-forward is possible.
          SQUASH Squashes the merged changes into one set and leaves them uncommitted.

      • Enum Constant Detail

        • MergeOp.Mode CREATE_COMMIT

          Always creates a merge commit (even if a fast-forward is possible). Behaves like --no-ff.

        • MergeOp.Mode DEFAULT

          Fast-forwards if possible, creates a merge commit otherwise. Behaves like --ff.

        • MergeOp.Mode NO_COMMIT

          Merges changes, but does not commit them. Behaves like --no-commit.

        • MergeOp.Mode ONLY_FF

          Only merges if a fast-forward is possible. Behaves like --ff-only.

        • MergeOp.Mode SQUASH

          Squashes the merged changes into one set and leaves them uncommitted. Behaves like --squash.
